data.description: This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom Craftsman style home is stunning! It features an open/split floor plan with 9 ft. ceilings throughout the home.  The kitchen has countertops made of Taj Mahal quartzite in a leather finish with custom built in shelving around electric fireplace in the living area and luxury vinyl flooring throughout the home. The fully fenced in backyard also has a large covered patio. Move in ready, this home won't disappoint!
